{"tid":1663562,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"銀髮族10.20結伴同行","createTime":"2019-10-19T13:10:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T02:43:20.000Z","uid":276684,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"6e86f8e3e824333388c9296350fe33180f145c91","tid":1663562,"uid":276684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T13:10:38.000Z","msg":"銀髮族 👨🏻&zwj;👵🏻&nbsp;10.20結伴同行<br />\n<br />\n我們提早集合一起，與年青人同行上街，為他們打打氣之餘，也是作為一個香港人應該要做的事。<br />\n<br />\n遊行從來都是人民應得的自由，我們仍然會以雙腳表達訴求。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，反抗！<br />\n<br />\n集合地點：<strong>尖沙咀鐘樓下</strong><br />\n時間：<strong>1:15pm</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">認住我地支旗呀...</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n*借網上圖<br />\n#和勇不分<br />\n#香港人反抗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6vUPeDX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6vUPeDX.jpg&h=f2ae9df7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wORYSqq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwORYSqq.jpg&h=4653b522&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/845348632510629/posts/914445352267623\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F845348632510629%2Fposts%2F914445352267623&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoCrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=f2eb76c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/845348632510629/posts/914445352267623</a>"},{"pid":"d359f0bd1fb95c4559b802c86bb5933954118ecc","tid":1663562,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T13:11:11.000Z","msg":"[1020 行動Post] 香港人真係好痴線！不論組織力、耐力、創意玩到咁！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eovgRS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eovgRS</a>"},{"pid":"2d3b4b96e510f4ed0123da94e7f5885c92b4dca3","tid":1663562,"uid":270237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T13:11:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UdDHzE4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F